"day_count": 1}, "62526": {"data": {"tag_id": 62526, "tag_name": "电子竞技", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/a2a72561d08920a244b789b76ebf09c40028e661.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/6b9942efbef31dd77ed49c492af34a32950efbcf.png", "content": "电子竞技（Electronic Sports）就是电子游戏比赛达到“竞技”层面的体育项目。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "2968": {"data": {"tag_id": 2968, "tag_name": "周杰伦", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/92b9ac40ec69192fe0fa2bcf932f0dc10eb295c8.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "周杰伦（Jay Chou），祖籍福建泉州。华语杰出音乐人、流行歌手、词曲创作家、制作人、MV电影导演、编剧，2000年后亚洲流行乐坛最具革命性创作歌手，唱片亚洲总销量超过3100万张，有“亚洲流行天王”之称，其音乐打破了亚洲原有单一的音乐主题形式，开创了多元化音乐创作和现代流行乐“中国风”的先河，为亚洲流行乐坛翻开了新的一页。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "386": {"data": {"tag_id": 386, "tag_name": "翻唱", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/192ee6bb1c5fb191a963711a6528376759cfe497.jpg", "head_cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/archive/92bceb592e8035bd01f8d1c89648e9896202aba1.jpg", "content": "“翻唱”是指将已经发表并由他人演唱的歌曲根据自己的风格重新演唱的演绎形式。", "short_content": "同一首好歌，不一样的精彩。", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "2621310": {"data": {"tag_id": 2621310, "tag_name": "TheShy", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 1, "state": 0, "ctime": 1473740146, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "254029": {"data": {"tag_id": 254029, "tag_name": "MOBA", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "217275": {"data": {"tag_id": 217275, "tag_name": "太阳之子", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 0, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "281": {"data": {"tag_id": 281, "tag_name": "MAD", "cover": "http://i0.hdslb.com/bfs/tag/88aae270ab94246268a6402c6af98e51308e87a4.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "MAD = M@D = MAD MOVIE\r\n它是电玩文化、动漫文化、同人文化界別中的多媒体作品。一般作品為一段有关的影片剪辑，配以作者喜欢的音樂，近似同人MV 形式的存在。不同的地方是MAD片的重点在于影片，对有关动画或电玩致敬，而相对同人MV的重点則放在音乐之上。当然亦有一些是只作声音的剪辑或只有画面的剪辑严格而言亦可算作MAD的。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 0}, "day_count": 1}, "4286": {"data": {"tag_id": 4286, "tag_name": "全明星", "cover": "http://i1.hdslb.com/sp/59/591629fcb1b3da4965b5008165f7ebaf_s.jpg", "head_cover": "", "content": "经常上NICONICO和BiliBili这类弹幕视频站的朋友想必对“全明星”一词并不陌生吧。\n　　说道全明星，一般都会想到鬼畜，鬼畜原本是一个贬义词,源自日语，原意指像魔鬼畜生一样残酷无情。\n　　而在NICONICO和BiliBili出现的全明星鬼畜类型MAD则多指通过视频（或音频）剪辑，用频率极高的重复画面（或声音）组合而成的一段节奏配合音画同步率极高的一类视频。", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0, "liked": 0, "hated": 0, "extra_attr": 1}, "day_count": 1}, "1907": {"data": {"tag_id": 1907, "tag_name": "二次元", "cover": "", "head_cover": "", "content": "", "short_content": "", "type": 3, "state": 0, "ctime": 1436866637, "count": {"view": 0, "use": 0, "atten": 0}, "is_atten": 0, "likes": 0, "hates": 0, "attribute": 0,